Why Choose Emory BBA
Get a glimpse into the BBA experience and what makes Goizueta special.
Apply to Goizueta
Emory undergraduate students may apply to the BBA program once they have earned enough credit hours to have junior standing and have completed BBA pre-requisites. High school students will need to apply directly to Emory University through the main Admissions Office.
Apply
Consultations
High school students and students newly admitted to Emory interested in business can meet one-on-one with our BBA Admissions team.
